title: Tuesday Post Show (04-05-22)
itunes:title: Tuesday Post Show (04-05-22)
description:
Bobby starts by talking about how much he loves Tractor Supply and the Top 3 Songs in Country Music. We play a game where Morgan can guess what band is Gun N’ Roses between 4 bands by seeing a picture. We take a roll through Bobby’s camera roll. We get into a discussion of deadly animals. We talk about what is considered a spoiler. Amy shares a story about her friend that was on a date and said something she couldn’t believe about his ex-girlfriend.
